CustomField.description: The API name of the end date field to use as the date to plot a record on the timeline. When provided, the record is displayed as a band rather than a plot point.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The API name of the end date field to use as the date to plot a record on the timeline. When provided, the record is displayed as a band rather than a plot point.
CustomField.label: End Date Field
